#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5241
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_BEAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"由传说中的，早已陨落的盐人帝国铸造的独一无二的武器。它发射一束高度压缩的气态盐束，对飞船造成轻微伤害，并毒害船员 50 "
"秒，每秒造成5点伤害。此光束会立即杀死蛞蝓。"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5335
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_SNIPER\"]/title"
msgstr "盐晶狙击炮"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5336
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_SNIPER\"]/short"
msgstr "盐晶狙击"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5337
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_SNIPER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"这把传说中的武器发射一发穿透所有护盾的弹体，造成3点舰体伤害与6点系统伤害，毒害船员10秒，每秒造成10点伤害。这把大炮会直接轰杀蛞蝓与无人机。"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5451
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_ION\"]/title"
msgstr "盐晶离子炮"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5452
